{
  "stem": "4247.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes, correct.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was living near the last bridge-- the-- the chain bridge, which was the last connecting link between Pest and Budapest.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as I was saying earlier, on the 18th of January '45, when the-- this was the last bridgehead for the Germans, through which they withdrew to the west, across the Danube.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a very cold winter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was January.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Danube was frozen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You could walk through the Danube quite safely.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "However, for the military equipment they needed, of course, a proper bridge.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And on-- on that night, at about 1 o'clock in the morning, a German party came in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were seemingly drunk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they said to their janitor that the house next door is-- is on fire.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And because the Germans had ammunition deposited there, if you don't extinguish this fire, we are going to blow up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The whole area will blow up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the women and the children came out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We formed a human chain.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were passing buckets full of water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I got a-- a rope-- because the house was damaged, next door.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no way of going up to that top floor, where the ammunition was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I just put a knot on it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I slung it up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It got caught somewhere.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I climbed up through that rope.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we-- And the other part of the rope was attached to buckets.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I pulled them up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And with that water, eventually I managed to extinguish that fire.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was a very, very precarious activity, because [LAUGH] I was amongst the explosives.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But-- luck-- whoever, whatever-- was looking after me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What motivated me?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very interesting question.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
